MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: What did you just say? Did Yours Truly misheard you...? Ohoho♪

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Like I said, hug and kiss each other～, quickly～

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: You'll make the people who are watching lose interest～ Strike while the iron is hot; Lewd while the brain is on dopamine--

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Wh-wh-wha-what are you talking about!?
After hearing Khajuraho spouting ridiculous stuff, Sentosa roared and backed away from her from shock.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Garwgh～! Wh-wha-wha-what do you mean kiss? Why? Nonsense, what are you on about!?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Ahaha! Sentosa, you're always bragging about how well you can study - But you don't know what a kiss is?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: I-I-I-I'm upset exactly because I know what it is!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: I don't see the point of such disgracefulness in this situation! And with Miss Jeran of all people--

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: ? Sentosa, don't you want to kiss Jeran...?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Of-of course not! Yo-you and Yours Truly and not in that kind of a relationship!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Oh～... What a pity～... Have been separated from Sentosa for a long time, and only recently have we been able to meet again--

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: in past, we had to part on bad terms. Thought we were now just normal friends who loved each other.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Ugh, uugh!?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: But, was Jeran wrong about that? After all, Jeran and Sentosa are a tiger and a lion, so we can't be friends...?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: W-wr-wrong! That's not what Yours Truly meant woi!? A-and don't look so sad lah, Jeran!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Y-Yours Truly does care about you! We did hurt each other once upon a time, and hopefully this time we can be friends who care for each other...!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Gaarrgh♪ So glad, thought Sentosa didn't like Jeran anymore! Because Sentosa is always lecturing, yeah?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Th-that's because you always have these nonsensical actions! I'm trying to teach a problem child like you properly--

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: A-as your friend, you should be guided in right direction...!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Friend? Eheeh, so Sentosa also considers Jeran a friend dah～?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Then that's very good dah～ Jeran is too dumb to say it properly, but this is really, really good dah～♪

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Jeran... Apologies, my dear, Yours Truly is so kiasu - Always hiding my embarrassment in vain, can't even convey important things properly.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: No, It's okay dah～ Surely you've got the message.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Really love Sentosa for always being so strong like that.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Really love the stubborn lion who acts proud, even when she's covered in scars so that no one can prey on her.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Jeran...

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Yours Truly too, Yours Truly is unlike you, you act noble and free, even when you're all alone -

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Garrrgh! Then let's kiss♪ It doesn't matter if we LOVE EACH OTHER DAH～!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: GYAAAAAAH!?
Jeran pounced on Sentosa like a wild beast. Caught off guard, Sentosa is pushed down without a second thought, and she flinched and struggled as hard as she could.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Gyaaa～! Gyaaaah!? Wha-wha-What are you doing, Jeran!?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: ? Like she said, we're going to kiss dah～ Khajuraho said so!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: J-just ignore what that siao lang says! We don't have to listen to her!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: And also what she said is all nonsense! K-Kissing in public..!? This is a lifelong shame, a disgrace, you'll regret it for sure!?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Hey! Is Yours Truly wrong for saying that!?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Yes yes～ Stop stalling and start kissing kay～? Some people are satisfied with just that, and they call it love, yet for others it's basically just foreplay!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: AR-ARE YOU GOING TO MAKE US DO MORE THAN THAAAT--!?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: ? What's more than that? Can you explain? Hard for Jeran now, but can still learn dah～♪

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: D-don't make Yours Truly explain it to you! STOOP-! HELP ME, DADDY, MOMMY, I'M BEING PLAYED WITH BY VILE BEASTS, HEEELP!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Khajuraho
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Wrong, wrong! Now is the time to teach the inhabitants of this town about the wonders of love, don't be disgusted, accept it properly! Rejoice!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: WHAT ON EARTH ARE YOU ON ABOUT!? YOU'RE INSANEEEE!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: --Papa, something's not right.
Asahikawa blurted out inexplicably while watching the rowdiness from afar.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: This is way too unusual regardless.

You're right, Khajuraho does regularly act vulgar most of the time, but she never does anything that could really hurt others. She's a professional preacher and tamer, she won't force someone to do something if they don't want to.

When Khajuraho first joined the SSS, due of differences in values and other factors, she sometimes repeatedly did things that hurt others. But after a number of unfortunate accidents, she had genuinely repented and reflected on her actions.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: That's part is strange, yes. However that tiger girl and the lion girl are also strange.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Jeran
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: GRRRAAH! GRRRAAH! GRRRAAH!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Sentosa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Gaurgh～! Gaurgh～! Stop, don't eat me, don't eat me! Don't eat Yours Truly～! I'm scareeeed!

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: ...The lion's condition is still okay, but the tiger's eyes appear insane. It's either their instincts are unleashed, or they're behaving like real beasts--

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: It may be possible she's just so excited that she lost her sense of self...

Indeed, it's strange. Jeran tends to behave like a savage, but she's a kind and gentle girl who loves her friends. There is no way that she would still treat Sentosa so badly after her own friend's crying and asking to stop.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Yeah. Maybe someone's will is intervening in their current actions.
What do you mean by 'someone'?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Someone that I don't know.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: I, too, have the ability to subdue animals. I used that ability to rule over my hometown - Doubutsuen.
I've heard about that. Asahikawa, do you have the mystical ability to control animals, similar to that of the demon-controller Fussen?

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Yeah. If those girls have lost their reason now, I might be able to manipulate them with that ability.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Nah. Maybe we can just stop the intervener and bring them back to their senses.
Asahikawa moved away from me regretfully and held up her gun gallantly. Then she ranted out, sounding annoyed as usual.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Listen, you stupid, dumb beasts.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: Obey me, the greatest and most kawaii girl in world.
Asahikawa fired her gun immediately after her cold announcement. The sound of gunshots and her voice echoed around the world - and immediately the ground of Sheep City began to tremble.

MSceneDetailViewModel.Name: Asahikawa
MSceneDetailViewModel.Phrase: What? Earthquake...?
'GETOUT GETOUT GETOUT!'

An eerie voice that sounds both male and female, flood in from the depths of the now shaking earth. It's an ear-grating voice, like a group of emotionally disturbed people speaking bitterly in unison.
'Why, are you interrupting me? Why, can't you understand? Why, why, why?'
'You know what's really going on, don't you?'
'Men with men! Women with women! That's the only true path to love...!'
Alongside the unintelligible cry, something rose up from below ground.
